38)Interpret the steps to iterate over a PHP array using a while loop with an example
&lt;?php
$fruits = array(&quot;Apple&quot;, &quot;Banana&quot;, &quot;Mango&quot;, &quot;Orange&quot;);
$i = 0;
$length = count($fruits);
while ($i &lt; $length) {
echo &quot;Fruit at index $i: &quot; . $fruits[$i] . &quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;;
$i++;
}
?&gt;
